{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Together with Souryuu\n\n<size=45>Chapter 4: Unnecessary Things...?<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Port - Sakura Dorms","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_room","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"On my day off, I once again found myself headed for Souryuu's room, looking to relax and recover.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Did you need to see my sister?","actor":307040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"Commander, though you're free to spend your day off however you please, I'd recommend you do something more worthwhile.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":307030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"As she spoke, she was still working on documents that she had brought back from the office yesterday. Truly a model secretary.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030,"bgName":"bg_story_room","withoutActorName":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"*sigh*...","actor":307040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I wonder when I'll be able to help the Commander like this...","actor":307040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"If that's what you really want, you'd better start studying harder from now on.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That's not what I meant... When you're working hard like this, you look really beautiful. Don't you think so too, Commander?","dir":1,"side":0,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"\"I agree.\""}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":307040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"*sigh*... What are you talking about? There's nothing beautiful about this.?","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Err, I dunno, I'm not so great with words... but Akagi said something about \"a woman's allure?\"","actor":307040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Listen, Hiryuu. This is simply what is expected of every member of the fleet. My relationship with the Commander has nothing to do with this.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"This has nothing to do with a \"woman's allure\" or that \"girlishness\" thing that you're always talking about, understood?","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Wow... Souryuu was being colder than usual.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307030,"bgName":"bg_story_room","withoutActorName":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Well, isn't there something that you'd want to do to improve your girlishness?","actor":307040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"What are you... why in the world would I want to do something like that?","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Ah, um, hear me out! I really think you're beautiful, Souryuu, and that includes when you're being cold too. However, I sometimes want to see more aspects of your personality!","actor":307040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"*sigh*...","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"But... Hmm. There just might be a way to get me to change.","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Eh? Really?!","dir":1,"side":0,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"\"I'd like to know, too.\""}],"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.15,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":307040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I wonder, what should I do...","actor":307030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Was it just my imagination, or did Souryuu just steal a sideways glance at me?","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"CANGLONG4","fadeOut":1.5}